hadiths[19]{hadithnumber,text}:
4235,"Leis ne hamein ibne-Shahab se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Ubaidullah bin-Abdullah se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se us nazar ke barey mein fatwa puchha jo unki walida ke zimma thi, wo usey pura karne se pahley hi faut ho gaee thin, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : usey unki taraf se tum pura karo."
4236,"Imam Malik, ibne-Uena, Younus, Mamar aur bikr-bin-Waail sab ne Zohri se Leis ki mazkura (uper zikr) sanad ke sath, unhi ki hadis ke ham mana hadis bayan ki."
4237,"Jarir ne Mansoor se, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Murra se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik din hamein nazar se mana karne lagey, aap farmaney lagey : ye kisi cheez ko nahi taalti , iske zariey se to kanjoos se ( Allah ki raah mein kuchh ( nikalwaayaa jata hai."
4238,"Abdullah-bin-Dinar ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : nazar kisi cheez ko aagey karti hai na peechhey , iske zariey se to kanjoos se (maal) nikalwaayaa jata hai."
4239,"Shoba ne hamein Mansoor se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Murra se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne nazar se mana kya aur farmaya : bila shubah ye koi khair lekar nahi aati, iske zariey se to kanjoos se (kuchh) nikalwaaya jata hai."
4240,Mufazzal aur Sufiyan donon ne Mansoor se isi sanad ke sath Jarir ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
4241,"Abdul-Azeez darawardi ne hamein Alaa se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : nazar na maana karo, nazar taqdeer ke mamley mein koi fayda nahi deti, iske zariey se to kanjoos se (maal) nikalwaaya jata hai."
4242,"Shoba ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Alaa se suna, wo apne walid se aur wo Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan kar rahe they, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne mannat manney se mana kya aur farmaya : ye taqdeer ke kisi faisley ko nahi taal sakti, iske zariey se to kanjoos se (maal) nikalwaaya jata hai."
4243,"Ismail bin Jafar ne hamein Amr bin abi Amr se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman Aaraj se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : bila shubah nazar kisi cheez ko ibne-Aadam ke qareeb nahi karti, jo Allah ne uske liye muqaddar nahi ki, balke nazar taqdeer ke sath muwafiqat karti hai, iske zariey se kanjoos se wo kuchh nikalwaaya jata hai jisey kanjoos nikaalna nahi chahta."
4244,Yaqoob bin Abdur-Rehman al-Qari aur Abdul-Azeez Darawardi donon ne Amr bin abi Amr se isi sanad ke sath isi ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
4245,"mujhey Zuhair-bin-Harab aur Ali-bin Hujr Sadi ne hadis bayan ki. padhi. alfaz Zuhair ke hain. padhi. un donon ne kaha hamein Ismail bin Ibrahim ne hadis sunai, kaha : hamein Ayub ne abu-Qilaba se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Mohlab se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Saqif, banu-Aqeel ke haleef (saathi) they, Saqif ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ashaab mein se do aadmiyon ko qaid kar liya, ( badley mein) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ashaab ne banu- Aqeel ke aik aadmi ko qaidi bana liya aur unhon-ne iske sath ontni azba bhi hasil kar li, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us aadmi ke paas se guzrey, wo bandha hua tha, usne kaha : aey Muhammad! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uske paas aaey aur puchha : kya baat hai? usne kaha : aap ne mujhey kis wjah se pakda hua aur haajiyon (ki sawaariyon) se sabqat ley janey wali ontni ko kyon pakda hai? aap ne. padhi. us mamley ko sangeen khayal kartey huey. padhi. jawab diya : maine tumhen tumharey haleef Saqif ke jurm ki bina par (iske izaaley ke liye) pakda hai. phir aap wahan se paltey to usne ( phir se) aapko awaz di aur kaha : aey Muhammad ! aey Muhammad ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahut raham karne waale, narm dil they. phir se aap uske paas wapas aaey aur farmaya : kya baat hai? usne kaha : ( ab ( mein musalman hun. aap ne farmaya : agar tum ye baat us waqt kehtey jab tum apne Malik aap they ( aazad they) to tum poori bhalai hasil kar letey ( ab bhi milegii lekin poori na hogi. ( phir aap paltey to usne aapko awaz di aur kaha : aey Muhammad ! aey Muhammad ! aap ( phir ( uske paas aaey aur puchha : kya baat hai? usne kaha : main bhooka hun mujhey ( khana ( khilaaiye aur piyaasa hun mujhey (pani) pilaaiye . aap ne farmaya : ( haan ( ye tumhari ( fauran poori ki janey wali) zarurat hai. iske baad) maamlaat tay karke ( usey donon aadmiyon ke badley mein chhod diya gaya. ( ontni peechhey reh gaee aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hissey mein aai. lekin mushrekeen ne dobara hamley karke phir usey apne qabzey mein ley liya. ( kaha : ( baad mein, jang zaatul-qird ke mauqe par, Madina par hamley ke doran) aik Ansari aurat qaid kar li gaee aur azba ontni bhi pakad li gaee, aurat bandhanon main ( jakdii hui ( thi. log apne oont apne gharon ke samney raat ko aaraam ( karne ke liye bitha ( detey they, aik raat wo ( khatun ( achcha bediyon ( bandhanon ( se nikal bhaagi aur oonton ke paas aai, wo ( sawari ke liye) jis oont ke bhi qareeb jati wo bilbilaaney lagta to wo usey chhod deti yahan tak ke wo azbaa tak pahunch gaee to wo na bilbilaai, kaha : wo sadhaai hui ontni thi to wo uski peeth ke pichhley hissey par baithi , aur usey daudaayaa to wo chal padi . logon ko us (ke janey (ka ilm ho gaya, unhon-ne iska ta'aqub kya lekin us ne unhein be bas kar diya. kaha is aurat ne Allah ke liye nazar maana ke agar Allah ne us ontni par usey nijat di to wo usey ( Allah ki raza ke liye) nehar kar degi. jab wo Madina pahunchi , logon ne usey dekha to kehney lagey : ye azbaa hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ontni . wo aurat kehney lagi ke usne ye nazar maana hai ke agar Allah ne usey us ontni par nijat ata farma di to wo us ontni ko (Allah ki raah mein) nehar kar degi. is par log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur aapko ye baat batai to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Subhan-Allah ! us aurat ne usey jo badla diya wo kitna bura hai ! us ne Allah ke liye ye nazar maana hai ke agar Allah ne usko us ontni par nijat de di to wo usey zabah kar degi, masiyat (gunah) mein nazar poori nahi ki ja sakti, na hi us cheez mein jiska banda Malik na ho. ibne-hijr ki riwayat mein hai : Allah ki masiyat mein koi nazar ( jaaiz ( nahi."
4246,"Hammad-bin-Zaid aur abdul-wahaab saqfi donon ne Ayub se isi sanad ke sath iske ham mana hadis bayan ki, Hammad ki hadis mein hai : unhon-ne kaha : azbaa ontni banu- Aqeel ke aik aadmi ki thi aur wo haajiyon ki sawaariyon mein sabse aagey rehney wali oontniyon mein se thi ( tez raftaar thi.) aur unki hadis mein ye bhi hai : aur wo ( qaidi aurat ( sadhaai hui mashshaaq ontni par) baith kar) aai , aur Saqafi ki hadis mein hai : wo sadhaai hui ontni thi."
4247,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik boodhey aadmi ko dekha wo apne do beton ke sahaarey chala kar ley jaya ja raha tha, aap ne puchha : iska kya mamla hai? logon ne kaha is ne paidal chalney ki nazar maana hai. aap ne farmaya : bila shubah Allah Taala us shakhs ke apne aapko azab deney se be-niyaaz hai. aur) uske paas paidal chal kar janey ki istitaat hi na thi, is liye) aap ne usey sawar honey ka hukm diya."
4248,"Yahya-bin-Ayub , Quteba aur ibne- hijr ne hamein hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Ismail-bin-Jafar ne Amr-bin-abi Amr se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman Aaraj se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik boodhey aadmi ko miley jo apne do beton ke darmyan , unka sahara liye chal raha tha to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha : iska mamla kya hai? iske donon beton ne kaha : Allah ke rasool ! iske zimmey nazar thi. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aey buzurg ! Sawar ho jao, Allah Taala tum se aur tumhari nazar se be-niyaaz hai) usey uski zarurat nahi. ( . padhi. alfaz Quteba aur ibne- hijr ke hain."
4249,"Abdul-Azeez darawardi ne Amr-bin-abi-Amr se, isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki."
4250,"Mufazzal-bin-fazaala ne hamein hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( mujhey Abdullah-bin-Ayash ne Yazeed-bin-abi-Habib se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abul-Khair se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aqba-bin-Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne kaha : meri behan ne nangey paon paidal chal kar Baitullah janey ki nazar maana aur mujh se kaha ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se uske liye fatwa loon , maine aap se fatwa puchha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : wo ( baqadr istitaat ( paidal chaley aur sawar ho."
4251,uper wali hadis isi sanad se marvi hai ‌.
4252,"Rauh bin Ubada ne hamein hadis bayan ki, (kaha :) hamein ibne-Juraij ne hadis sunai, (kaha : ( mujhey Yahya bin Ayub ne khabar di ke unhein Yazeed bin abi Habib ne isi sanad se khabar di. padhi. Abdur-Razzaq ki hadis ki tarah ."
4253,"Hazrat Aqba-bin-Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya : nazar ka kaffara ( wahi hai jo ( qism ka kaffara hai."
